Walang sumusunod sa akin!

244
00:20:41,419 --> 00:20:42,879
Walang sumusunod sa iyo.

245
00:20:58,102 --> 00:21:00,313
Ayan, maganda!

246
00:21:01,314 --> 00:21:02,732
Napaka refreshing!

247
00:21:03,608 --> 00:21:07,445
Sigurado akong walang mang-iistorbo sa akin dito.

248
00:21:08,988 --> 00:21:10,406
Tawagin ko ang brat na iyon.

249
00:21:22,126 --> 00:21:23,503
Hindi siya sasagot.

250
00:21:27,307 --> 00:21:28,490
Ugh!

251
00:21:29,192 --> 00:21:30,193
Fuck!

252
00:21:30,218 --> 00:21:31,260
Sino yun?

253
00:21:32,845 --> 00:21:35,056
Ay, Edrix!

254
00:21:35,681 --> 00:21:37,391
Akala ko ibang tao!

255
00:21:37,600 --> 00:21:38,893
Anong ginagawa mo dito?

256
00:21:45,900 --> 00:21:47,109
Paumanhin.

257
00:21:47,777 --> 00:21:49,237
Hindi ko lang napigilan.

258
00:21:52,824 --> 00:21:53,991
may problema ka ba?

259
00:21:57,161 --> 00:21:58,371
Galit ako sa sarili ko!

260
00:21:59,997 --> 00:22:01,082
Napaka duwag ko!

261
00:22:03,543 --> 00:22:04,560
Bakit?

262
00:22:06,546 --> 00:22:08,923
Ang unrequited love ay makatarungan
so damn hard!

263
00:22:09,090 --> 00:22:10,466
Hindi ko man lang masabi sa kanya...

264
00:22:11,467 --> 00:22:12,718
o ipakita sa kanya.

265
00:22:16,013 --> 00:22:17,557
Oo, mahirap talaga.

266
00:22:18,683 --> 00:22:20,768
Pero at least sigurado ka.

267
00:22:21,352 --> 00:22:22,687
Ito ay isang tao lamang.

268
00:22:23,104 --> 00:22:26,399
Mas mahirap kapag suplado ka
sa pagitan ng dalawa.

269
00:22:30,194 --> 00:22:31,863
Ngunit sino pa rin ito?

270
00:22:37,785 --> 00:22:40,454
Wow, ang ganda niya!

271
00:22:41,080 --> 00:22:42,373
Ang ganda talaga ni Freya.

272
00:22:42,874 --> 00:22:45,543
Oo, siya talaga—ANO?

273
00:22:47,753 --> 00:22:48,838
Si Freya yun?

274
00:22:52,300 --> 00:22:53,776
F-Si Freya kasi
pinag-uusapan mo?

275
00:22:53,801 --> 00:22:54,819
Oo.

276
00:22:54,844 --> 00:22:56,037
Matagal na Jay.

277
00:22:57,638 --> 00:23:00,433
Wow, anong rebelasyon.

278
00:23:01,434 --> 00:23:02,560
Pero...

279
00:23:03,269 --> 00:23:04,854
Itago natin ito sa pagitan natin, okay?

280
00:23:05,980 --> 00:23:07,045
Pangako?

281
00:23:19,076 --> 00:23:20,328
Wala kang pagkain?

282
00:23:21,913 --> 00:23:22,496
Pagkain yan?

283
00:23:22,580 --> 00:23:25,141
Oo, kumakain kami sa ibaba.

284
00:23:25,166 --> 00:23:26,717
At dito ka madrama.

285
00:23:37,970 --> 00:23:38,779
kanino ito?

286
00:23:38,804 --> 00:23:41,390
- Tita, nagugutom na talaga ako promise.
- Mukhang ito.

287
00:23:41,557 --> 00:23:43,184
Huwag mag-alala, may isa pang kahon doon.

288
00:23:43,184 --> 00:23:44,518
Lahat ng yan ay para sayo.

289
00:23:44,810 --> 00:23:45,853
May bisita tayo?

290
00:23:46,312 --> 00:23:49,023
Relax, marami pa sa kusina.

291
00:23:49,857 --> 00:23:51,108
- Napakasarap nito, Auntie.
- Mabuti?

292
00:23:51,359 --> 00:23:52,373
Ci-N?

293
00:23:55,738 --> 00:23:56,781
Idiot ka!

294
00:23:56,948 --> 00:23:58,201
Anong nangyari sayo?

295
00:23:58,616 --> 00:24:01,077
Alam mo ba kung paano
nag-aalala ako, brat ka?!

296
00:24:01,285 --> 00:24:02,119
talaga?

297
00:24:02,119 --> 00:24:03,310
Nag-aalala ka sa akin?

298
00:24:03,496 --> 00:24:05,831
Wow, ang sweet mo, Jay.

299
00:24:06,123 --> 00:24:07,500
Wag kang ganyan, Jay-jay!

300
00:24:07,500 --> 00:24:08,501
Sorry po, Auntie.

301
00:24:08,834 --> 00:24:10,336
Ang batang ito ay hindi pumasok sa paaralan ngayon.

302
00:24:12,088 --> 00:24:14,548
Iiwan ko kayong dalawa para maghabol.

303
00:24:14,715 --> 00:24:16,092
Maghahanda ako ng hapunan.

304
00:24:16,133 --> 00:24:17,343
Salamat po, Auntie.

305
00:24:20,972 --> 00:24:22,306
May lakas ng loob ka!

306
00:24:22,348 --> 00:24:23,516
Masyadong nag-eenjoy sa pagkain, ha?

307
00:24:23,516 --> 00:24:24,475
Bakit wala ka sa klase?

308
00:24:24,517 --> 00:24:25,366
Ang sakit, Jay!

309
00:24:25,391 --> 00:24:26,810
- Oh talaga!
- Sasabihin ko kay Auntie!

310
00:24:27,186 --> 00:24:28,451
Anong nangyari sayo?

311
00:24:32,984 --> 00:24:34,026
Ano ang problema?

312
00:24:36,237 --> 00:24:37,240
Dahil…

313
00:24:38,114 --> 00:24:39,532
ikinulong ako ng kapatid ko.

314
00:24:40,574 --> 00:24:41,584
Sabi niya...

315
00:24:42,034 --> 00:24:44,954
pinapunta niya ako sa London
dahil patuloy akong nagdudulot ng gulo.

316
00:24:45,246 --> 00:24:47,331
Sinabi kong sinasayang ko ang aking potensyal.

317
00:24:48,082 --> 00:24:49,667
Syempre
Hindi ko iyon papayagan.

318
00:24:49,667 --> 00:24:52,211
Kaya oo,
ikinulong niya ako sa kwarto ko.

319
00:24:54,171 --> 00:24:55,673
Nag-alala ako sayo.

320
00:24:57,133 --> 00:24:57,800
Paumanhin...

321
00:24:57,800 --> 00:24:59,677
Kinumpiska niya ang mga gadget ko,

322
00:24:59,677 --> 00:25:00,803
Hindi ako nakapag-message sa iyo.

323
00:25:01,262 --> 00:25:02,680
Iyon lang ba ang ginawa niya?

324
00:25:03,014 --> 00:25:03,931
Hindi ka niya sinaktan?

325
00:25:03,931 --> 00:25:04,949
Hindi!

326
00:25:04,974 --> 00:25:05,850
Alam mo kung bakit?

327
00:25:05,850 --> 00:25:06,308
Bakit?

328
00:25:06,308 --> 00:25:07,601
Dahil tumakas ako.

329
00:25:08,394 --> 00:25:09,895
- Seryoso?
- Oo.

330
00:25:10,396 --> 00:25:13,274
Sinabi niya kung hindi ako makinig,
Dapat umalis na lang ako.

331
00:25:13,983 --> 00:25:15,609
Saan ka pupunta?

332
00:25:15,776 --> 00:25:16,777
Dito. kasama mo!

333
00:25:16,986 --> 00:25:18,879
Bawal yan, baliw ka?!

334
00:25:18,904 --> 00:25:20,698
Bakit hindi?
Okay lang daw sabi ni Angelo.

335
00:25:20,698 --> 00:25:21,949
Anong Angelo?

336
00:25:22,033 --> 00:25:22,867
Ginawa mo yan!

337
00:25:22,867 --> 00:25:24,827
Tama Angelo, okay lang?

338
00:25:25,119 --> 00:25:26,287
Oo, totoo iyon.

339
00:25:26,996 --> 00:25:28,789
Oh—kita mo?

340
00:25:29,957 --> 00:25:31,542
Masakit yun!

341
00:25:39,759 --> 00:25:41,010
Ang bago kong tahanan.

342
00:25:44,180 --> 00:25:45,473
Hindi ka ba nila hahanapin?

343
00:25:45,681 --> 00:25:47,141
Hindi, alam ni Nanay.

344
00:25:47,141 --> 00:25:48,217
sabi ko sa kanya.

345
00:25:48,350 --> 00:25:49,351
Wow.

346
00:25:49,810 --> 00:25:51,604
Sa lahat ng taong umalis sa bahay, ikaw
ang tanging humingi ng permiso.

347
00:25:51,604 --> 00:25:52,288
Kahanga-hanga.

348
00:25:52,313 --> 00:25:53,981
Syempre—
kaya alam ni Nanay kung saan ako pupunta.

349
00:25:56,650 --> 00:25:58,123
Saan ka pa matutulog?

350
00:25:58,486 --> 00:25:59,695
Sabi ni Angelo sa kwarto mo.

351
00:26:00,029 --> 00:26:01,197
kwarto ko?

352
00:26:02,364 --> 00:26:03,741
- Gusto mo ba?
- Oo.

353
00:26:04,366 --> 00:26:06,077
Race mo sa kwarto mo!

354
00:26:06,077 --> 00:26:08,829
Idiot! Bawal kumain dyan!

355
00:26:08,829 --> 00:26:09,830
Hoy!

356
00:26:09,914 --> 00:26:10,920
Ci-N!

357
00:26:13,042 --> 00:26:15,795
[Kumakanta si Ci-N]

358
00:26:23,677 --> 00:26:25,054
Ci-N!

359
00:26:39,985 --> 00:26:42,238
Magandang umaga po.

360
00:26:44,365 --> 00:26:47,284
Bumangon ka na!
Basang-basa ang unan mo sa laway mo.

361
00:26:59,004 --> 00:26:59,922
Ci-N, ang ingay mo!

362
00:26:59,922 --> 00:27:01,173
Kaya madaling araw!

363
00:27:09,849 --> 00:27:10,558
Mauuna na ako, Jay.

364
00:27:10,558 --> 00:27:11,642
Bumaba para kumain.

365
00:27:16,939 --> 00:27:19,692
Wow, feel at home.

366
00:27:30,202 --> 00:27:31,217
Ouch.

367
00:27:51,390 --> 00:27:53,017
May ginawa ba sayo si Aries?

368
00:27:56,770 --> 00:27:58,898
ano? Ano ang ginawa niya?

369
00:28:03,819 --> 00:28:04,935
Tara na.

370
00:28:04,987 --> 00:28:06,006
ha?

371
00:28:19,126 --> 00:28:22,296
Ci, teka—kausapin mo ako.

372
00:28:22,838 --> 00:28:24,882
Anong ginawa sayo ni Aries?

373
00:28:25,883 --> 00:28:26,951
Totoo ba, Jay?

374
00:28:27,259 --> 00:28:28,474
Aalis ka sa Section E?

375
00:28:30,221 --> 00:28:31,764
Sinabi ba sayo ni Aries yan?

376
00:28:32,723 --> 00:28:36,352
Sabi niya layuan ko daw
mula sa iyo dahil aalis ka.

377
00:28:37,728 --> 00:28:39,538
Hindi, huwag mo akong layuan.

378
00:28:39,563 --> 00:28:41,523
- Baliw.
- Huwag makinig sa kanya.

379
00:28:42,024 --> 00:28:43,108
Sino nagsabi niyan?

380
00:28:43,683 --> 00:28:45,143
Sinong nagsabing aalis ka sa Section E?

381
00:28:47,947 --> 00:28:48,756
Sino ang lumalaban?

382
00:28:48,781 --> 00:28:50,157
may sabong ba?

383
00:28:50,241 --> 00:28:52,409
Jay, aalis ka sa Section E?

384
00:28:53,035 --> 00:28:54,511
Hindi!

385
00:28:54,536 --> 00:28:56,205
Pero yun ang sabi niya!

386
00:28:56,413 --> 00:28:58,499
Bakit niya sasabihin iyon?

387
00:28:58,791 --> 00:29:00,459
Ayaw mong kasama
tayo na ba, Jay?

388
00:29:00,501 --> 00:29:02,753
Matitiis pa rin namin ang maasim mong ugali.

389
00:29:02,836 --> 00:29:05,005
Akala ko solid Section E kami.

390
00:29:05,172 --> 00:29:07,424
- Aray!
- Oo.

391
00:29:07,633 --> 00:29:11,428
Akala namin walang makakasira sa amin.

392
00:29:11,637 --> 00:29:13,138
- Eksakto.
- Napakadrama!

393
00:29:13,138 --> 00:29:14,323
Hindi ito ganoon!

394
00:29:14,348 --> 00:29:15,357
Si Aries ba?!

395
00:29:16,100 --> 00:29:17,685
Keifer, tumigil ka!

396
00:29:17,685 --> 00:29:20,396
Jay, wag kang umalis!
Manatili sa Seksyon E!

397
00:29:20,396 --> 00:29:22,189
- Huwag kang umalis!
- Ci, sapat na!

398
00:29:22,189 --> 00:29:23,707
- Wala akong pakialam!
- Jay, huwag naman!!

399
00:29:23,732 --> 00:29:25,042
Ano bang nangyayari dito?!

400
00:29:25,067 --> 00:29:26,819
Aalis na si Jay-jay sa Section E!

401
00:29:26,986 --> 00:29:28,112
- Tumigil ka!
- Jay, pakiusap!

402
00:29:28,112 --> 00:29:29,129
totoo ba yun?

403
00:29:29,154 --> 00:29:29,905
hindi ako!

404
00:29:29,905 --> 00:29:31,740
Tingnan mo—magpapaliwanag ako mamaya!

405
00:29:31,740 --> 00:29:34,535
Puntahan mo muna si Keifer,
baka habulin niya si Aries! Magmadali!

406
00:29:34,868 --> 00:29:36,704
- Ci, walang aalis!
- Jay pakiusap!

407
00:29:36,704 --> 00:29:37,871
hindi ako aalis!

408
00:29:39,415 --> 00:29:40,624
- Napakadrama!
- Talaga?

409
00:29:40,865 --> 00:29:42,784
Oo! Yan ang sinasabi ko!

410
00:29:43,002 --> 00:29:44,211
Sinabi sa akin ni Aries na pumili:

411
00:29:44,211 --> 00:29:45,462
Alinman sa aalis ako sa Section E,

412
00:29:45,462 --> 00:29:47,298
o hindi niya ako bibigyan
number ng Dad ko.

413
00:29:47,298 --> 00:29:50,009
Pero pinili ko kayo, okay?!
Masaya ngayon?!

414
00:29:50,384 --> 00:29:52,511
Tara na, kailangan nating sundan si Keifer!

415
00:29:52,511 --> 00:29:53,554
Magmadali!

416
00:29:53,595 --> 00:29:55,681
- Tayo na!
- Ayoko na! Bakit?

417
00:29:55,681 --> 00:29:57,349
Binabayaran mo ba ako para dito?
ayoko na!

418
00:30:01,061 --> 00:30:02,107
Bumangon ka na!

419
00:30:12,865 --> 00:30:13,881
Halika dito.

420
00:30:31,925 --> 00:30:33,385
Ganun ba, ha?!

421
00:30:40,309 --> 00:30:41,602
Tara na, dali!

422
00:30:44,938 --> 00:30:46,690
ano?
Tapusin na natin ito dito ngayon!

423
00:30:46,690 --> 00:30:47,608
Okay, tapusin na natin dito.

424
00:30:47,608 --> 00:30:48,484
May makakapigil ba sa kanila?!

425
00:30:48,484 --> 00:30:51,111
Tama na!
Tumigil ka na!

426
00:30:51,362 --> 00:30:54,698
Sa palagay ko ay totoo ang mga sabi-sabi,
ang gulo talaga dito.

427
00:30:55,240 --> 00:30:57,534
Makakaalis na ba ang mga talunan dito?

428
00:30:57,534 --> 00:30:58,202
Lalo na ikaw!

429
00:30:58,243 --> 00:31:00,871
Tama na!
Huwag kang magsalita ng ganyan kay Jay-jay!

430
00:31:01,080 --> 00:31:02,748
Jay-jay, kailangan mo nang umalis.

431
00:31:03,040 --> 00:31:05,013
Ang mga bagay ay lumalabas
kontrolin dahil sa iyo.

432
00:31:08,754 --> 00:31:09,974
As if naman.

433
00:31:10,714 --> 00:31:12,257
Tumigil ka na, tara na.

434
00:31:12,674 --> 00:31:14,134
Hindi hanggang sa magmura ka!

435
00:31:14,301 --> 00:31:16,678
Magmura sa harap ni Aries,
hindi mo kami iiwan!

436
00:31:18,639 --> 00:31:19,848
Ngayon na!

437
00:31:24,396 --> 00:31:25,397
Paumanhin.

438
00:31:33,612 --> 00:31:34,947
Sorry, Aries.

439
00:31:37,324 --> 00:31:39,660
Nasabi ko na ito dati,
at sasabihin ko ulit.

440
00:31:41,161 --> 00:31:42,830
Hindi ako aalis sa Section E.

441
00:31:47,584 --> 00:31:48,710
Oo!

442
00:31:48,794 --> 00:31:50,318
Hindi ka ba makukuha ng karma niyan?

443
00:31:50,587 --> 00:31:52,005
Desisyon mo yan.

444
00:31:52,005 --> 00:31:54,007
Sana hindi ka magsisi.

445
00:31:55,092 --> 00:31:57,386
Nawalan ka lang ng pagkakataon
kasama mo ang iyong ama.

446
00:31:59,596 --> 00:32:00,806
Napakatanga!

447
00:32:02,933 --> 00:32:05,060
Yan ang pang-blackmail mo kay Jay-jay?

448
00:32:07,771 --> 00:32:09,273
Nakakalimutan mo na ba kung sino ako?

449
00:32:09,565 --> 00:32:11,066
Lagi kong nakukuha ang gusto ko.

450
00:32:12,317 --> 00:32:13,365
Tss.

451
00:32:16,363 --> 00:32:16,989
Huwag kang mag-alala, Jay.

452
00:32:16,989 --> 00:32:19,366
Pangako gagawin ko
ikonekta ka sa iyong ama.

453
00:32:49,146 --> 00:32:51,064
Paano mo nalaman na nandito ako?

454
00:32:51,655 --> 00:32:55,117
Uhh, sabi ni Edrix tambay ka
dito para magpahangin.

455
00:32:57,863 --> 00:33:00,657
Wala pang isang linggong klase,
pero nakipag away ka na.

456
00:33:05,954 --> 00:33:07,122
Sumakit ang mga kamay ko.

457
00:33:08,081 --> 00:33:09,249
Gawin mo para sa akin.

458
00:33:18,800 --> 00:33:19,776
Aray!

459
00:33:19,801 --> 00:33:21,011
Maging banayad!

460
00:33:21,762 --> 00:33:24,389
Sinong nagsabing makipag-away ka noon?

461
00:33:24,848 --> 00:33:26,183
Laging nawawalan ng galit.

462
00:33:32,523 --> 00:33:33,549
pasensya na po.

463
00:33:36,151 --> 00:33:39,530
Wow!
Ang galing mo mag-sorry, ha.

464
00:33:39,821 --> 00:33:40,739
"I'm sorry".
Sabihin mo ulit.

465
00:33:40,739 --> 00:33:42,324
Isa pa, halika na.
Isang beses pa.

466
00:33:42,324 --> 00:33:43,617
Tigilan mo na ang pagpapatawa sa akin.

467
00:33:43,742 --> 00:33:45,077
Humihingi lang ako ng tawad sa iyo.

468
00:33:45,994 --> 00:33:47,162
Bakit ako lang?

469
00:33:47,162 --> 00:33:49,998
Sigurado ako na mayroon kang mahabang listahan ng mga tao
kailangan mong humingi ng tawad.

470
00:33:49,998 --> 00:33:51,917
Sino ang una?
Aries, at pagkatapos—

471
00:33:51,917 --> 00:33:53,043
Wala akong pakialam.

472
00:33:53,377 --> 00:33:55,295
Wala akong nararamdaman kahit kanino sa kanila.

473
00:33:56,171 --> 00:33:57,256
Para lang sayo.

474
00:34:10,811 --> 00:34:11,893
kahit ano!

475
00:34:15,440 --> 00:34:16,858
Mangyaring manatili.

476
00:34:25,951 --> 00:34:27,703
Mangyaring manatili.

477
00:34:28,078 --> 00:34:29,096
Keifer...

478
00:34:37,087 --> 00:34:38,755
Hindi ako sumusuko sayo, Jay.

479
00:34:42,509 --> 00:34:44,094
Ipaglalaban kita.

480
00:34:57,899 --> 00:34:59,359
Anong klaseng panaginip iyon?

481
00:35:00,444 --> 00:35:04,406
Hindi iyon nangyari,
pero parang totoo.

482
00:35:05,907 --> 00:35:08,452
Tama na, Jay-jay!

483
00:35:14,449 --> 00:35:16,993
Magandang umaga, Jay! See you.

484
00:35:27,387 --> 00:35:28,416
Ci-N?

485
00:35:44,696 --> 00:35:45,881
Nauna na ako, Jay!

486
00:35:45,906 --> 00:35:48,283
Imposibleng magising ka,
patuloy ka lang sa pag-ungol.

487
00:35:49,326 --> 00:35:50,369
Shit!

488
00:35:53,538 --> 00:35:55,499
Mababaliw talaga ang brat na yan
galing sa akin mamaya.

489
00:35:57,376 --> 00:35:59,086
Iniwan niya talaga ako?

